    <title>Health Insurance as Economic Stimulus? Evidence from Long-Term Care Jobs</title>
    <updated>2025-02-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Martin B. Hackmann, Jörg Heining, Roman Klimke, Maria Polyakova &amp; Holger Seibert</name>
